<p><iframe src="http://scp-wiki-cn.wikidot.com/log-of-anomalous-items-cn:00436/?theme_url=http://scp-wiki-cn.wdfiles.com/local--code/log-of-anomalous-items-cn:_theme/1" align="" frameborder="0" height="" scrolling="no" width="" class="" style="width:100%;height:26px;overflow:hidden"></iframe></p>
<p><strong>项目描述：</strong>一把M1911手枪。使用时，将枪口对准一名手中持有任意复杂器械的人员，按下扳机后项目将使目标手中的复杂器械被解体成零件。<br />
<strong>回收日期：</strong>20██/██/██<br />
<strong>回收地点：</strong>混沌分裂者三号哨站<br />
<strong>当前状态：</strong>无效化。<br />
<strong>笔记：</strong><em>以后不准有人随便拿异常照镜子，除非经过了授权。</em></p>
<div style="text-align: right;">
<p><span id="u-credit-00436" class="option-button fa fa-info-circle">信息</span><a class="option-button fa fa-edit" href="/log-of-anomalous-items-cn:00436" target="_blank">编辑</a></p>
</div>
<div id="u-credit-00436-hovertip">
<p><strong>作者：</strong><span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/chris-evertworth" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(6285604); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=6285604&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1610200733" alt="Chris Evertworth" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=6285604)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/chris-evertworth" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(6285604); return false;">Chris Evertworth</a></span></p>
<p><strong>发布日期：</strong><span class="odate time_1602166748 format_%25Y-%25m-%25d">08 Oct 2020 14:19</span></p>
</div>
